Case 1:20-cr-00330-AJN Document 141 Filed 02/04/21 Page 1 of 2

UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT
SOUTHERN DISTRICT OF NEW YORK
---------------------------------------------------------------X

UNITED STATES OF AMERICA,

v.

GHISLAINE MAXWELL,
Defendant.

20 Cr. 330 (AJN)
NOTICE OF MOTION
ORAL ARGUMENT REQUESTED
---------------------------------------------------------------X

DEFENDANT GHISLAINE MAXWELL'S NOTICE OF MOTION TO DISMISS SUPERSEDING INDICTMENT FOR BREACH OF NON-PROSECUTION AGREEMENT
(Pretrial Motion # 1)

PLEASE TAKE NOTICE that, upon the accompanying memorandum of law and exhibits, Defendant Ghislaine Maxwell, through counsel, hereby moves to dismiss the superseding indictment for breach of the non-prosecution agreement.

Dated: January 25, 2021
New York, New York

Respectfully submitted,
